{"word":"ἐνίσχω","slug":"ἐνίσχω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐνίσχω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>= <a href='S:ἐνέχω'><el>ἐνέχω</el></a>\n<p/><a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a>, <el>ἐνίσχεσθαι τὴν φωνήν</el> <i>to keep in one's</i> voice, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be held fast</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/>"}]}